text: Ane ame isra'ilana santanane raheva mate uttama thekanum apyum ane ame temane khava mate pavitra vastu'o api, temane virodha na karyo tyam sudhi ke temani pase jnana pahonci gayum, kharekhara tamaro palanahara te'oni vacce kayamatana divase te babato vise nirnaya karase, jena vise te'o virodha karata hata
